  }), mdx("h3", null, "Work"), mdx("p", null, "On Tuesday I did something new for the first time. And I feel like I failed miserably. I hosted a webinar. Back in the beginning of the year, I sent out proposals to a bunch of conferences with the goal of giving a talk. A conference by ", mdx("a", {
